@sig 313a9654
export registerLocal(t,e)→registerDnsSd,tryAvahi,registerMcast|route mDNS registration to dns-sd(mac)|Avahi(linux)|Node.js mcast
registerDnsSd(e,r)→String,t,n.unref,n.kill|spawn dns-sd process for Bonjour service registration
tryAvahi(e)→t,r.on,r.unref,r.kill|spawn avahi-publish-address process for Linux mDNS registration
registerMcast(t)→t.split,Buffer.alloc,e.write,n.map,Buffer.from,Buffer.concat|create UDP socket and send mDNS answer packets
PATTERNS: platform-specific mDNS implementation fallback
EDGE_CASES: silently ignores UDP errors|kills spawned processes on cleanup
